{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was, there were edicts out that you could-- laws that you could only go out in the working force, I think, 16 or 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to be 16 or 18.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, I was 11, and we went into, as I said, the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, when-- the Aktions, the Aktions, where they separated people to-- and killed them off were going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the big one was only-- you know, and as I said, I think it was November or-- and thereafter, there were small separations and killings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you encounter any yourself?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I encountered them separate-- you know, drive-- every time we were driven out of our homes into the streets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans would come through and look through who, who-- especially they pick the ones who were old and sick.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they would separate them immediately and kill them off, take them out and-- again, under the camouflage that they were just sending them to better headquarters for better care, to hospitals and so on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, then eventually, within, I would say, half a year, we were-- the, the population, the Jewish population dwindled.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were put into the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the, the small ghetto was, was closed off, partitioned off, because they didn't need so much room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember then we went to live in another house in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that house I remember quite distinctly was downstairs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had-- there was a kitchen immediately upon entrance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To the right was my Aunt Paula.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a bedroom there, and she lived there with her two children because one was-- had died in the big Aktion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] past the kitchen was another room.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
